Description:
On the road you meet an old dwarf who is throwing small runestones over and over again, when you approach he says:

"Ohhh some new adventurers in these lands, if you answer my riddle maybe I can read your future:

A dragon leaves Velkarath heading south at a constant speed of twenty pegasi per hour, and a griffin leaves Senenthia with the same speed heading north... what would the dragon have eaten for breakfast?"
